name: UAE NFT. United Arab Emirates
description: NFT country UAE. The base is made of solidified processed oil from the United Arab Emirates itself, to which various precious stones and crystals have been added. The base holds through the most famous Dubai building and the World's tallest "Burj Khalifa" made of high-grade dark gold standing on a gold bar. Stand made of gold with a special texture. On the stand, you can see the division into: on the right - the desert and on the left-a developed and rich city of gold, next to the famous 5-star hotel Burj Al Arab, and between the desert and the city of glass, an oil pump working with a mechanism. All this suggests that the Arabs were able to achieve huge development with the help of oil and tourism and become one of the richest countries in the world.
